description: Lists the schemas for relations within a collaboration.

parameters.name: collaborationIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the collaboration that the schema belongs to. Currently accepts a collaboration ID.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name for the schema object.

nested_items.name: creatorAccountId
nested_items.description: The unique account ID for the Amazon Web Services account that owns the schema.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time the schema object was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The time the schema object was last updated.

nested_items.name: collaborationId
nested_items.description: The unique ID for the collaboration that the schema belongs to.

nested_items.name: collaborationArn
nested_items.description: The unique ARN for the collaboration that the schema belongs to.

nested_items.name: analysisRuleTypes
nested_items.description: The types of analysis rules that are associated with this schema object.

nested_items.name: analysisMethod
nested_items.description: The analysis method for the associated schema.

nested_items.name: selectedAnalysisMethods
nested_items.description: The selected analysis methods for the schema.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token that's used to fetch the next set of results.
